<p>I use earth often, because runners cant come up to me once I nuke. Earth also has lots of hp but sadly they have low dex and agility, so they are almost always hit.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br /> <br />I also use fire a lot. Its DS is pretty good and it has nice damage. It doens't have much hp but at level 8 you can heal your pets, so it's not a problem. <br /> <br />I think water is ok. They have hp too, and are immune to poison. But they dont have too much punch and they still get hit pretty often. <br /> <br />Air, I think is useless except for fighting casters. For newbies, unless you want to get rid of your fire or earth or water pet and summon an air pet every time you want to fight an oracle at the orc lift, air is pretty useless. In LDON it would be good against the chanties, but other then that I think air is pretty useless. <br /></p>
